Useful ECharts Debug Example
============================

if (!data || !data.series || !data.series[0]?.fields) {
  console.error("No data found");
  return { series: [] };
}

const fields = data.series[0].fields;

console.table(
  fields.map(f => ({
    name: f.name,
    did: f.labels?.did,
    string: f.labels?.f,
    value: f.values.get(0)
  }))
);


Quick Summary
=============

console.log()       -> Normal print
console.table()     -> Table display
console.error()     -> Error message
console.warn()      -> Warning message
console.info()      -> Information
console.dir()       -> Deep object view
console.count()     -> Count executions
console.time()      -> Measure speed
console.group()     -> Group logs
console.clear()     -> Clear console
console.assert()    -> Validate conditions
